The How It Works Book of Great Inventors & Their Creations is a celebration of some of the people whose brilliant minds and perseverance have helped shape the modern world. They are by no means the only geniuses in history, nor are they the only great inventors. But the people whose biographies feature in this book are icons in the history of technology.
